rows.label: qst500208_msg0001
rows.name:
Foorara never been in place
like this before!

rows.label: qst500208_msg0002
rows.name:
Is very empty and backward- ah,
Foorara mean quaint and rural village.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0003
rows.name:
Even more calm and relax
than Gula!

rows.label: qst500208_msg0004
rows.name:
When being here, is like ruckus of
Invidia and Superbia just bad dream.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0005
rows.name:
Climate nicer than Luxuria, too.
Very good for living.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0006
rows.name:
This place so nice, Foorara wonder
why everyone not come here.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0007
rows.name:
Anyway, Voltis Trade Guild Walky-
Walky Guide Book say, after visit eight
region, Walky-Walky is complete!

rows.label: qst500208_msg0008
rows.name:
Sad to end journey, but Foorara go
back now to Voltis Trade Guild.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0009
rows.name:
Friends keep Foorara company lots
along way, so maybe should drop by
Voltis and Foorara prepare little thanks!

rows.label: qst500208_msg0011
rows.name:
Oh, Foorara understand.
Voltis Trade Guild too far away
for friends to come get thanks.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0012
rows.name:
That is shame. Foorara wanted to
show friends local Shark Gecko.

rows.label: qst500208_msg0013
rows.name:
OK, how about... Foorara wait for
friends on Goldmund Flight Deck.
How that sound?
